<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Welcome to Task Tracker</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f4f4f4; margin: 0; padding: 0;">
    <table style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; background-color: #fff; border-radius: 5px;">
        <tr>
            <td style="text-align: center; padding: 20px 0;">
                <img src="https://img.freepik.com/premium-vector/white-clipboard-task-management-todo-check-list-efficient-work-project-plan-fast-progress-level-up-concept-assignment-exam-productivity-solution-icon-3d-vector-render-white-background_412828-739.jpg?w=2000" alt="Task Tracker" width="150">
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td style="padding: 20px;">
                <h2>Welcome to Task Tracker</h2>
                <p>Dear <%= @user.name %>,</p>
                <p>Thank you for joining Task Tracker! We're excited to have you as a member of our community.</p>
                <p>With Task Tracker, you can easily manage your tasks, set priorities, and stay organized.</p>
                <p><strong>Your login details:</strong></p>
                <p><strong>Email:</strong> <%= @user.email %></p>
                <p><strong>Password:</strong> <%= @user.password %></p>
                <p>Feel free to explore our site and get started with managing your tasks.</p>
                <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, please don't hesitate to contact our support team at ritikd@shriffle.com .</p>
                <p>Thank you again for choosing Task Tracker!</p>
                <p>Best regards,<br>The Task Tracker Team</p>
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td style="background-color: #007BFF; padding: 10px; text-align: center;">
                <p style="color: #fff; font-size: 14px; margin: 0;">&copy; 2023 Task Tracker</p>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>
</body>
</html>
